{"tid":1124253,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【復仇者聯盟】喵星人是黑豹祖先？","createTime":"2019-04-25T02:28:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T03:03:55.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"854dcdcd7532632b929bcbb2a8fac0c81e490b1e","tid":1124253,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T02:28:21.000Z","msg":"電影《復仇者聯盟》的終章於今天（24日）正式上映，迎來最終結局。這齣電影讓全球戲迷引頸期盼已久，不但在網上引起熱烈討論，就連預售電影門票的網站也因太多人進入而癱瘓，可見其人氣之高。<br />\n<br />\n日本有網民於Twitter發起了有關《復仇者聯盟》的Hashtag，但這次的主角並非帥氣的電影角色們，而是與電影角色們「撞樣」的動物。Twitter名稱為「beniko71」的網民首先發起#アニマルアベンジャーズ（Animal Avengers）的Hashtag，並分享了多張動物相片。相中的動物們神情威武，就連姿勢也跟《復仇者聯盟》中的角色十分相似。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2714840/org/689290ae6d909c3f2ace06b97602031f.JPG/1n4fREupNxgRCDufW1P19l1wPtTTPt6roVVqMaFVajE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2714840%2Forg%2F689290ae6d909c3f2ace06b97602031f.JPG%2F1n4fREupNxgRCDufW1P19l1wPtTTPt6roVVqMaFVajE&h=aa61ee1f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2714846/org/7b78e874c64a81d820abbc061ad21b81.jpg/VT7nFlYX6tYBvhqCxadzkfk4J_7pibLfCqqsNwqqrDc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2714846%2Forg%2F7b78e874c64a81d820abbc061ad21b81.jpg%2FVT7nFlYX6tYBvhqCxadzkfk4J_7pibLfCqqsNwqqrDc&h=b809da03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2714852/org/265b6869b0705ba3b61636271c26b679.JPG/pF1qzrmDzugJDE3cRYvJ_zWR7BOsUTQbOHT8NDh0_DQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2714852%2Forg%2F265b6869b0705ba3b61636271c26b679.JPG%2FpF1qzrmDzugJDE3cRYvJ_zWR7BOsUTQbOHT8NDh0_DQ&h=d711fe2d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2714845/org/028f4ec14c9edfaf278d7c12c41fe343.jpg/QaJxPy03F4L2Pwy8y_x5astZlEjqMI81kcoCrJHKAqw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi